OL,3,CHistoric lido could reopen by the
OL,4,Cmiddle of August
OL,6,FWork to upgrade a historic lido in
OL,7,FStroud has now started with the hope
OL,8,Fthat the pool can reopen to the public
OL,9,Fin the middle of August.
OL,11,FThe latest update from Stroud District
OL,12,FCouncil reveals a target date of 14
OL,13,FAugust, although there is potential
OL,14,Ffor Stratford Park Lido to reopen on
OL,15,F29 July if everything goes smoothly.
OL,17,FContractors took control of the site
OL,18,Fon Thursday May 28 and have started
OL,19,Fcarrying out preliminary work.
