OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1780150315
OL,3,CHistoric lido could reopen by the
OL,4,Cmiddle of August
OL,6,FThe council has set aside more than
OL,7,F#200,000 for repair and maintenance
OL,8,Fwork, although councillors will meet
OL,9,Fnext Wednesday (June 3) to decide
OL,10,Fwhether to approve additional funding
OL,11,Fof #276,000 which would allow the 90-
OL,12,Fyear old lido to reopen this summer.
OL,14,FCouncil Leader Chloe Turner said: "We
OL,15,Fknow how important the Lido is to our
OL,16,Fresidents and how much people want to
OL,17,Fsee it open again.
OL,26,@vD@cOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
