OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1780150315
OL,3,CHistoric lido could reopen by the
OL,4,Cmiddle of August
OL,6,F"This latest update provides a clear
OL,7,Fpicture of the work required and the
OL,8,Ftimeline we are working to. The
OL,9,Fextraordinary meeting gives
OL,10,Fcouncillors the opportunity to
OL,11,Fcarefully consider the options and
OL,12,Fmake a decision as quickly as possible.
OL,14,F"This approach ensures proper
OL,15,Fdemocratic oversight while giving the
OL,16,Fproject the best possible chance of
OL,17,Fsuccess.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
