CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1780150315
OL,3,CHistoric lido could reopen by the
OL,4,Cmiddle of August
OL,6,F"I am grateful to council officers,
OL,7,Flocal councillors and volunteers from
OL,8,Fthe community for doing everything
OL,9,Fthey can to help achieve an opening
OL,10,Ffor this summer."
OL,12,FIn its latest update the council said
OL,13,Fthe latest timetable couldn't be
OL,14,Fguaranteed as it was subject to
OL,15,Ffunding being approved, and no
OL,16,Fadditional repair work being
OL,17,Fidentified.
